  &lt;Comment&gt;
    &lt;CommentText&gt;Thank you for your comments.

We apologies for how you felt recently at one of your last visits to Salford Royal. We hope we can assure you that the Trust strives to provide patients with excellent care, so we are disappointed that we did not achieve it for you on this occasion.

We would also like to re-assure you that PALS works hard to respond to all queries as soon as they can so again we are disappointed we did not meet your expectations on their response to you. We will notify the team so they can look into their procedures. 

As your review is anonymous, to re-address your concerns we will again have to ask you to get in touch with PALS quoting you have been advised to do so via the NHS Website. They can be contacted on 0161 206 2003 or via email to pals@srft.nhs.uk between the hours of 08:30 and 16:30, Monday to Friday.

Kind regards
The Patient Experience Team
